--- Freecomerce Webshop ----
---- @author lants1 --------
##########################
Used Technologies:
##########################
PHP5
MySQL
fpdf17 included in php/lib
smarty-3.1.17 include in php/lib

##########################
Setup Environment
##########################

1. copy the whole project to your htdocs Folder of your Webserver
2. setup the db with the scripts under freecomerce/db folder user: demo1 pw: demo1 db:freecomerce
3. use a high quality browser and enjoy the shop:)